European Stocks Decline as BHP, Rio Fall; Stoxx 600 Index Retreats 0.4%

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-03-09T16:02:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/european-stocks-decline-as-bhp-rio-fall-stoxx-600-index-retreats-0-4-.html
European stocks declined, dragging
the Stoxx Europe 600 Index 0.4 percent lower to 280.62 as of
4:01 p.m. in  London . BHP Billiton Ltd. and Rio Tinto Group led
raw-material shares lower on the gauge.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
